WEBVTT

00:04:59.204 --> 00:05:02.496
The only way to really achieve
all of your dreams

00:05:02.538 --> 00:05:05.788
is to fully enjoy every step
of your journey.

00:05:06.454 --> 00:05:07.621
That's the best way.

00:05:07.621 --> 00:05:09.996
And your journey is simple --
it's made of steps.

00:05:10.038 --> 00:05:11.954
Some steps will be right on.

00:05:11.996 --> 00:05:13.538
Sometimes you will trip.

00:05:14.204 --> 00:05:18.829
If it's right on, celebrate, because
some people wait a lot to celebrate.

00:05:18.829 --> 00:05:21.954
And if you tripped,
turn that into something to learn.

00:05:21.996 --> 00:05:27.413
If every step becomes something
to learn or something to celebrate,

00:05:27.454 --> 00:05:29.496
you will for sure enjoy the journey.